oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Union captain's shoulder insignia
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Union captain's shoulder insignia originally belonging to Capt. James E. White, the last commander of Ft. Negley. White served in the 12th Ind. Lt. Arty., USA.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Tennessee State Library and Archives, Nashville, Davidson County, Tennessee
